article_title: Dora PD searching for missing person possibly in danger
article_text:
Police in Dora are searching for a missing person who may be in danger.

Officers are searching for Nicholas Hawkins. He told his family someone was trying to harm him the last time they spoke to him, according to investigators.

His vehicle was located at a home in Dora Sunday evening.

Anyone with information about this case should contact Dora police.
